This program will do the following.

1.First it will let a person create an Account and then ask them to create a password.
2.After they create an account,they will be asked to login.
3.If login is successful,it will ask them to enter their name,email id,etc.
4.If login is unsuccessful,it will ask them to try again.


Classes :
1.Details.
    Variables:-
    name;
    email;
    address;
    school;
    TechSkills[];

    Methods:-
    getName();
    setName();
    getEmail();
    setEmail();
    getAddy();
    setAddy();
    getSchool();
    setSchool();
    getTechSkills();
    setTechSkills();

2.User (extends details) :
    Variables:-
    uid;
    pass;

    Methods:-
    getUid();
    setUid();
    getPass();
    setPass();
